DescriptionData.Title: Magnetic Screen Door, Mosquito Patio Screens Automatic closing Full Frame with Heavy Duty Velcro French Mesh Curtain Insect Screen Mesh
DescriptionData.Description:
At AIWKR we strive to make your life easier.

Magnetic Fly Screen Door, can be installed in every house entrance in just a few minutes!

Keeps insects away, lets in fresh air and your pet can freely enter and exit the house whenever you want.


【Features】:
1. Tightly woven mosquito net which blocks out flies as well as possible.
2. Made from high-quality polyester, more tear-resistant and durable.
3. Enhanced magnetic power. Always seals completely.
4. Free up your hands while opening it.
5. Wide range of applications. E.g. balcony door, bedroom, kitchen, children's room.

【How to install】:
1. Please clean your door frame surface before stick Velcro on it.
2. Measure length of your door top and left and right side frame.
3. Stick Velcro on top of door frame first, then on both sides frame, carefully peeling.
4. Start from top center of door frame, firmly pressing Velcro along to left and right side.

【Package included】: 
1 x Magnetic Screen Door 
1 x magic tape roll

【Service】: If you have any questions, please contact us by email first, thank you!
DescriptionData.BulletPoint: GOODBYE INSECTS: Keep annoying insects outside with a fly screens. This mosquito insect screen lock these flying creatures out, protects you against infectious diseases and mosquito and insect bites.
FRESH AIR IN: This magical mosquito door net is gas-permeable and transparent. Open the door, and enjoy fresh air without flies.
WHAT IT DOES：This Fly Door Screen with magnetic closure can be attached easily to your balcony door, bedroom, kitchen, children's room or sliding door.
HANDSFREE: Allows easy walking when your hand is full. Pet Friendly, Dogs and cats can easily access the interior and exterior of the house. Screen net helps keep insects, mosquitoes and flies OUT!
EASY INSTALLATION: There is long sticky magic tape coming with the curtain. You could attach the curtain to the door fame without any tools.

At AIWKR we strive to make your life easier.

Magnetic Fly Screen Door, can be installed in every house entrance in just a few minutes!

Keeps insects away, lets in fresh air and your pet can freely enter and exit the house whenever you want.


【Features】:
1. Tightly woven mosquito net which blocks out flies as well as possible.
2. Made from high-quality polyester, more tear-resistant and durable.
3. Enhanced magnetic power. Always seals completely.
4. Free up your hands while opening it.
5. Wide range of applications. E.g. balcony door, bedroom, kitchen, children's room.

【How to install】:
1. Please clean your door frame surface before stick Velcro on it.
2. Measure length of your door top and left and right side frame.
3. Stick Velcro on top of door frame first, then on both sides frame, carefully peeling.
4. Start from top center of door frame, firmly pressing Velcro along to left and right side.
